{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001","id":"msg_01R64AJPzKAWnGji7vZ8Ncca","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Based on my analysis of the code and test case, I've identified the root cause of the memory error. Let me create a summary:\n\n## ROOT CAUSE\n\n**peglib.h:2563** — When a non-macro rule calls a macro, `FindReference` is initialized with the wrong parameter vector. The line uses `c.rule_stack.back()->params` (the calling rule's parameters) instead of `rule_->params` (the called macro's parameters). This causes a vector size mismatch: when visiting arguments in the loop at line 2842-2843, if `args_.size() > params_.size()`, `params_[i]` accesses out-of-bounds memory.\n\nIn the test case:\n- Rule `A` (non-macro) calls `B(T)` where `B` is a macro\n- When processing the call, `params_` is set to `A.params = []` (empty)\n- But `args_` contains `[T]` (size 1)\n- The loop `for (size_t i = 0; i < args_.size(); i++)` tries to access `params_[0]` which is out of bounds\n\n## LOCAL FIX\n\nChange line 2563 from:\n```cpp\nFindReference vis(c.top_args(), c.rule_stack.back()->params);\n```\n\nto:\n```cpp\nFindReference vis(c.top_args(), rule_->params);\n```\n\nThis ensures `FindReference` uses the parameter names of the **macro being called**, not the current rule, so argument sizes are properly aligned.\n\n## GLOBAL FIX\n\nAdd a bounds check in the `FindReference::visit(Reference &ope)` method (line 2841-2850) to prevent out-of-bounds access:\n```cpp\ninline void FindReference::visit(Reference &ope) {\n  for (size_t i = 0; i < args_.size() && i < params_.size(); i++) {\n    const auto &name = params_[i];\n    if (name == ope.name_) {\n      found_ope = args_[i];\n      return;\n    }\n  }\n  found_ope = ope.shared_from_this();\n}\n```\n\nThe primary fix (changing to `rule_->params`) addresses the root cause; the secondary bounds check provides defense-in-depth against similar mismatches elsewhere in the codebase."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":7,"cache_creation_input_tokens":874,"cache_read_input_tokens":73019,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":874},"output_tokens":4,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":{"cache_miss_reason":{"type":"unavailable"}},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"7bbe0357-5a81-44ba-b67d-d1dfa22d5642","uuid":"6d22ef07-d5ff-4bc2-bc59-e9ffbdfb63b4"}
